      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014well-maintained and ready for many more miles of adventures! It's got a few tiny character marks here and there from some great road trips, but it still runs super smooth. If you're looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road, you've gotta come take this for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
