      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the legendary S54-powered coupe. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features a recently serviced VANOS system and updated rod bearings for long-term reliability. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a variable M differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced. The chassis is dialed in with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, preserving the communicative steering and neutral handling balance the platform is known for. A well-maintained driver's car ready for the canyon or the track.",
